code: export function parseJwt(token){if(!token){return;}const base64Url=token.split('.')[1];const base64=base64Url.replace('-','+').replace('_','/');return JSON.parse(window.atob(base64));}export const handleLogError=error=>{if(error.response){console.log(error.response.data);}else if(error.request){console.log(error.request);}else{console.log(error.message);}};
